== 制作 ==
1984年，导演罗伯·莱纳、制片人安德鲁·沙因曼和编剧诺拉·艾芙伦一起在[[纽约|纽约]]的一家餐馆吃午饭，并探讨开发一个项目<ref name="keyser" />。莱纳提出一个提议，但艾芙伦没有接受<ref name="dvd1">{{cite news | title = It All Started Like This | work = When Harry Met Sally... Collector's Edition DVD | publisher = 20th Century FOX | year = 2008}}</ref><ref name = "ASIN_B000XJD33O">{{ASIN|B000XJD33O|title=When Harry Met Sally... (Collector's Edition) (1989)}}</ref>。他们的第二次会面变成了对莱纳和沙因曼单身汉生活的漫长讨论。莱纳对此回忆道，“那时候我单身，已经离婚了一段时间，出门约过几次会，一个接一个的都是些灾难性的混乱关系。”<ref name="weber">{{cite news | last = Weber | first = Bruce | title = Can Men and Women Be Friends? | work = New York Times | date = 1989-07-09 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1989/07/09/movies/film-can-men-and-women-be-friends.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103161519/http://www.nytimes.com/1989/07/09/movies/film-can-men-and-women-be-friends.html | archive-date = 2012-11-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>三人再下一次会面时，莱纳表示自己一直想拍一部有关两个人成为朋友并坚持不做爱，因为他们知道这会毁掉两人的关系，但最后还是做了的电影。艾芙伦很喜欢这个点子，而莱纳则与一间公司达成了协议<ref name="keyser"/>。

艾芙纳接下来开始对莱纳和沙因曼进行采访，了解他们的生活，为接下来的剧本创作提供素材。这些采访也为哈利一角提供了基础。莱纳经常感到郁闷，悲观但又很搞笑。 艾芙伦还从采访里截取了一些内容作为剧本中的台词。莎莉一角则是基于艾芙伦自己和她的一些朋友<ref name="keyser" />。 她在莱纳拍摄《[[伴我同行_(電影)|伴我同行]]》和《{{link-en|公主新娘 (电影)|The Princess Bride (film)|公主新娘}}》期间写了好几稿剧本<ref name="dvd1" />。比尔·克里斯托加入时，项目名称为《男孩认识女孩》，他对剧本给出了自己的建议，让哈利一角更具喜剧色彩<ref name = "ASIN_B000XJD33O" /><ref name="dvd2">{{cite news | title = When Rob Met Billy | work = When Harry Met Sally... Collector's Edition DVD | publisher = 20th Century FOX | year = 2008}}</ref>。克里斯托当时是莱纳最好的朋友，对后者与[[潘妮·马歇尔|潘妮·马歇尔]]离婚后回归的单身生活有一定了解，这一过程不知不觉就成了哈利一角的研究基础<ref name="keyser" />。

在剧本撰写过程中每当艾芙伦感觉自己不想写作时，就会去采访制片公司的工作人员。其中部分内容以情侣接受采访谈到两人如何认识的形式穿插在电影的特定场景中<ref name="keyser"/>，不过相应内容有经过改写，并且是另外找演员来拍摄的。艾芙伦的剧本中有许多台词都是基于莱纳和克里斯托在现实生活中的对话<ref name="lacey">{{cite news | last = Lacey | first = Liam | title = Pals make "buddy picture" | work = The Globe and Mail | date = 1989-07-15}}</ref>。例如，片中莎莉和哈利出现在两个分割镜头，一起煲电话聊起各自在看的电视及换的频道这些内容，就曾是克里斯托和莱纳每晚的固定节目<ref name="lacey"/>。

艾芙伦一开始打算给电影起名为《他们怎么认识的》（{{lang|en|How They Met}}），并先后换过多个标题。莱纳甚至于主体拍摄在剧组人员中展开了一场竞赛：想出名片的那位可以赢得一箱[[香槟酒|香槟]]<ref name="dvd1" />。为了表现出哈利离婚后单身期间孤独的心态，电影在[[曼哈顿|曼哈顿]]拍摄期间克里斯托都会单独呆在一个房间里，而不是与别的演员一起<ref name="lacey"/>。起初剧本的结局是男、女主角仍然是朋友，没有进一步发展浪漫关系，因为编剧和导演都觉得这才是“真正的结局”<ref name="dvd1" />。最终，两人意识到让哈利和莎莉结婚作结尾更合适，虽然他们都认为这种结果通常是不现实的<ref name="featurette">{{cite news | last = Schwarz | first = Jeffrey | title = How Harry Met Sally... | work = When Harry Met Sally DVD | publisher = MGM | year = 2000}}</ref>。

对于电影的核心问题，男人和女人能否只做朋友，瑞安回答，“是的，男人和女人可以只做朋友。我有一大堆柏拉图式的（男性）朋友，性爱并不会成为拦路虎。”克里斯托回答，“我比哈利要更乐观一点。但我也觉得这很难。男人基本上就像超市门前的流浪狗。我是有些柏拉图式的（女性）朋友，但不是最最最好的朋友。”<ref name="peterson">{{cite news | last = Peterson | first = Karen S | title = When boy meets girl | work = USA Today | date = 1989-07-17}}</ref>

罗伯·莱纳起初的设想是请{{link-en|苏珊·黛|Susan Dey}}出演莎莉·艾尔布莱特一角。遭到拒绝后，他又考虑过[[伊丽莎白·帕金斯|伊丽莎白·帕金斯]]和[[伊丽莎白·麦戈文|伊丽莎白·麦戈文]]。导演本已基本确定要请[[莫利·林沃德|莫利·林沃德]]，但梅格·瑞安说服了他由自己来出演。

=== 餐馆镜头 ===
[[File:Whenharry3.jpg|缩略图]]
[[File:Harry_und_Sally_bei_Katz'_Deli.JPG|缩略图]]
片中两位主角一起在曼哈顿的一家餐馆吃午饭，他们对男人是否能辨认出女人是在[[假高潮|假装性高潮]]的问题起了争执。莎莉声称男人分辨不出来，为了证明这一点，她生动地现场假装高潮，也伴隨著[[叫床|呻吟聲]]，身上的衣服沒有脫下，不过整个餐厅里的人都在看着。然后莎莉漫不经心地继续吃她点的菜，而旁边的一位老妇人（由莱纳的母亲埃斯特尔扮演）下了订单，“我要点和她一样的”（{{lang|en|I'll have what she's having}}）。2008年，埃斯特尔以94岁高龄去世，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》称她“说出了电影史上最令人难忘的好笑台词”<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/30/movies/30reiner.html |title=Estelle Reiner, 94, Comedy Matriarch, Is Dead |publisher=New York Times |date=2008-10-29 |accessdate=2013-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108140558/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/10/30/movies/30reiner.html |archive-date=2014-01-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。这个镜头拍了很多次，瑞安示范了自己的假高潮达几个小时<ref name="featurette"/>。这家餐馆之后一直挂着这么一个挂牌，“当哈利遇到莎莉，希望你得到她那般的享受！”<ref>{{cite web | url=http://guestofaguest.com/new-york/movies/12-nyc-spots-used-in-famous-movie-scenes&slide=1 | title=12 NYC Spots Used In Famous Movie Scenes: Katz's Delicatessen | publisher=[[Guest_of_a_Guest|Guest of a Guest]] | accessdate=2013-12-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224103040/http://guestofaguest.com/new-york/movies/12-nyc-spots-used-in-famous-movie-scenes%26slide%3D1# | archive-date=2013-12-24  }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | url=https://news.yahoo.com/katzs-delicatessen-yorks-famous-unique-deli-181400732.html | title=Katz's Delicatessen: New York's Famous, Unique Deli | work=[[Yahoo!_News|Yahoo! News]] | date=2013-04-01 | accessdate=2013-12-23 | last=Holden | first=Eric | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131224120049/http://news.yahoo.com/katzs-delicatessen-yorks-famous-unique-deli-181400732.html | archive-date=2013-12-24 }}</ref>

这个经典镜头的产生源于电影过多地聚-{焦}-在哈利身上。克里斯托记得当时说过，“‘我们需要给莎莉安排一些谈资’，而诺拉说，‘好啊，假高潮就很好啊，’这个主题不错，然后梅格也过来了，我们就和她谈这个点子的本质啊之类东西，而她说，‘我干脆就直接装一个呗，就一个？’”<ref name="keyser" />瑞安建议这个镜头在一家餐馆中拍摄<ref>Ephron (?) speaking on [http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/ BBC Radio 4] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/radio4/ |date=20130713194841 }} programme ''[http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00m6zpr When Harry Met Sally At 20] {{Wayback|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b00m6zpr |date=20160715053600 }}'' (aired 2009-08-27), about 17 mins in</ref>，而“我要点和她一样的”这句台词则是克里斯托想出来的<ref name="keyser" />。莱纳记得电影試映的时候，所有的女性观众都在大笑，而所有的男性观众都很沉默<ref name="dvd1" />。

== 电影音乐 ==
《当哈利碰上莎莉》的电影配乐唱片包含有美国歌手兼钢琴家小亨利·康尼克的作品。鼓手鲍比·哥伦拜（{{lang|en|Bobby Colomby}}）是导演的朋友，他向莱纳推荐小亨利·康尼克并给了他一盘录有后者音乐的磁带。莱纳对康尼克的嗓音非常满意，觉得与年轻时的[[法兰·仙纳杜拉|法兰·仙纳杜拉]]极其相似<ref name = "ASIN_B000XJD33O" /><ref name="dvd3">{{cite news | last = Reiner | first = Rob | coauthors = Nora Ephron, Billy Crystal | title = DVD Audio Commentary | work = When Harry Met Sally... Collector's Edition DVD | publisher = 20th Century FOX | year = 2008}}</ref>。电影配乐的唱片由[[哥伦比亚唱片|哥伦比亚唱片]]于1989年7月发行，其中包括小亨利·康尼克的多段表演，马克·施艾曼编排了一个[[大乐团|大乐团]]和[[管弦乐团|管弦乐团]]。康尼克为此赢得了自己的第一座[[葛莱美奖|葛莱美奖]]<ref name="grammy">
{{cite news | title = Past Winners Search | publisher = The Recording Academy | url = http://www.grammy.com/nominees/search?artist=&title=&year=1989&genre=All | accessdate = 2008-01-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120321142209/http://www.grammy.com/nominees/search?artist=&title=&year=1989&genre=All | archive-date = 2012-03-21 | dead-url = no }}
</ref>。

片中的《{{lang|en|It Had to Be You}}》、《{{lang|en|Where or When}}》、《{{lang|en|I Could Write a Book}}》和《{{lang|en|But Not for Me}}》四首歌是由康尼克与施艾曼部署和编排的。其他歌曲则要么是[[钢琴|钢琴]]/[[人声|人声]]独唱，要么是康尼克与另外两位音乐家的三重奏。唱片中还包括了[[次中音萨克斯风|中音萨克斯演奏家]]弗兰克·威斯（{{lang|en|Frank Wess}}）和吉他演奏家乔伊·伯林格（{{lang|en|Joy Berliner}}）演奏的曲目。这张唱片登上了《[[告示牌_(杂志)|告示牌]]》传统爵士榜榜首，并在[[公告牌二百强专辑榜|公告牌二百强专辑榜]]中排入前50位<ref>{{cite news | last = Jones | first = James T | title = Harry Connick Jr.: He's All That Jazz | work = USA Today | date = 1989-12-28}}</ref>。康尼克还为宣传这张唱片在北美进行了巡演<ref>{{cite news | last = Miller | first = Mark | title = Brazilian rhythms with lots of appeal ''When Harry Met Sally...'' Harry Connick Jr. | work = The Globe and Mail | date = 1989-11-23}}</ref>。唱片已经达到了[[RIAA认证|双白金认证]]<ref>{{cite news | last = Bush | first = John | title = Harry Connick Jr. Biography | publisher = Biography.com | url = http://www.biography.com/people/harry-connick-jr-5542 | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130521011616/http://www.biography.com/people/harry-connick-jr-5542 | archive-date = 2013-05-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

电影中的曲目由多位艺术家表演，如[[路易斯·阿姆斯特朗|-{zh-hans:路易斯·阿姆斯特朗;zh-hk:路易斯·岩士唐;zh-hant:路易斯·阿姆斯壯;}-]]、[[艾拉·费兹洁拉|艾拉·费兹洁拉]]、法兰·仙纳杜拉、[[雷·查尔斯|雷·查尔斯]]、[[冰·哥罗士比|冰·哥罗士比]]和小亨利·康尼克。

== 反响 ==
=== 票房 ===
[[哥伦比亚电影公司|哥伦比亚电影公司]]首先选择在少数几个城市放映本片，等到电影的正面口碑引起观众们的兴趣时，再在之后几个星期里逐渐扩大上映范围。《当哈利碰上莎莉》首周在41家电影院上映，收入为100万美元<ref name="boxoffice">{{cite news | title = When Harry Met Sally... | publisher = Box Office Mojo | url = http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=whenharrymetsally.htm | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130802180737/http://boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=whenharrymetsally.htm | archive-date = 2013-08-02 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。比利·克里斯托担心电影会在票房上遭遇惨败，因为当时上映的有多部像《[[圣战奇兵|圣战奇兵]]》和《[[蝙蝠侠_(1989年电影)|蝙蝠侠]]》这样的暑期大片<ref name="keyser">{{cite news | last = Keyser | first = Lucy | title = It's Love at the box office for ''Harry Met Sally...'' | work = Washington Post | date = 1989-07-25}}</ref>。影片于1989年7月21日开始大范围上映，首周在775家电影院入账880万美元<ref name="boxoffice" />，之后扩张到1174家电影院，最后在北美地区获得的票房总额为9280万美元，远远超出了其1600万美元的预算<ref name="boxoffice" />。

=== 专业评价 ===
《当哈利碰上莎莉》上映后获得了普遍的好评。根据[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上收集的70篇评论文章，其中63篇给出了“新鲜”的正面评价，“新鲜度”为90%，平均得分8.03（最高10分）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/when_harry_met_sally/ |title=When Harry Met Sally (1989) |publisher=Rotten Tomatoes |accessdate=2020-04-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200417153249/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/when_harry_met_sally |archive-date=2020-04-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，而在[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]上根据17篇评论文章为电影打出了76分（满分100）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/when-harry-met-sally |title=When Harry Met Sally... |accessdate=2013-07-13 |work=Metacritic |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121024060743/http://www.metacritic.com/movie/when-harry-met-sally |archive-date=2012-10-24 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《[[芝加哥太阳报|芝加哥太阳报]]》影评专栏作家[[罗杰·埃伯特|罗杰·埃伯特]]称赞莱纳是“好莱坞最优秀的喜剧导演之一”，电影有“符合我们预期的最为常规的结构和方式。但其特别之处除了艾芙伦的剧本外，还有着克里斯托和瑞安的化学反应”<ref>{{cite news|last=Ebert |first=Roger |title=When Harry Met Sally . . . |work=Chicago Sun-Times |date=1989-07-12 |url=http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/when-harry-met-sally---1989 |accessdate=2013-07-12 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130602193947/http://www.rogerebert.com/reviews/when-harry-met-sally---1989 |archivedate=2013-06-02 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的卡恩·詹姆斯（{{lang|en|Caryn James}}）称本片是一部“通常很有趣但却空洞得惊人的电影”，认为影片把“聪明、成功又神经兮兮纽约人的生活浪漫主义化”。詹姆斯将其特点概括为“[[伍迪·艾伦|伍迪·艾伦]]电影的情景喜剧版，充满了有趣的台词和镜头，但又全部注入了一种‘似曾相识’的不舒服的感觉”<ref>{{cite news | last = James | first = Caryn | title = It's Harry (Loves) Sally in a Romance Of New Yorkers and Neuroses | work = New York Times | date = 1989-07-12 | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1989/07/12/movies/review-film-it-s-harry-loves-sally-in-a-romance-of-new-yorkers-and-neuroses.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140313205549/http://www.nytimes.com/1989/07/12/movies/review-film-it-s-harry-loves-sally-in-a-romance-of-new-yorkers-and-neuroses.html | archive-date = 2014-03-13 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

《[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]》的丽塔·肯伯莉（{{lang|en|Rita Kempley}}）在评论中称赞梅格·瑞安是“夏天的[[梅拉尼·格里菲思|梅拉尼·格里菲思]]……她既不天真也不是个荡妇，她是一个女人笔下的女人，不是什么《[[上班女郎|上班女郎]]》中的[[灰姑娘|灰姑娘]]”<ref>{{cite news | last = Kempley | first = Rita | title = Romance That Dances | work = Washington Post | date = 1989-07-12 | url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/whenharrymetsallyrkempley_a0c9a5.htm | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105102142/http://www.washingtonpost.com/wp-srv/style/longterm/movies/videos/whenharrymetsallyrkempley_a0c9a5.htm | archive-date = 2012-11-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[今日美国|今日美国]]的麦克·克拉克（{{lang|en|Mike Clark}}）给予电影三星的评价（最高四星），他写道，“克里斯托的风趣幽默让瑞安不至于从全方面抢了他的风头，而她则给出了令人大开眼界的表演，是又一个莱纳选择演员天赋的绝佳体现”<ref>{{cite news | last = Clark | first = Mike | title = ''Harry Met Sally'' is Reiner's next sure thing | work = USA Today | date = 1989-07-12 | url = http://pqasb.pqarchiver.com/USAToday/access/55933280.html?FMT=ABS&FMTS=ABS:FT&date=Jul+12%2C+1989&author=Mike+Clark&pub=USA+TODAY+(pre-1997+Fulltext)&edition=&startpage=01.D&desc=%60Harry+Met+Sally%27+is+Reiner%27s+next+sure+thing |accessdate=2013-07-12}}</ref>。不过，《[[新闻周刊|新闻周刊]]》的大卫·安森给出了较为负面的评价。他批评导演选择克里斯托来出演，“他对喜剧的处理表现毫不令人感到意外，但作为一部浪漫爱情片的男主角，他太过冷酷和自我保护了”。安森觉得这部电影中精彩的部分没能起到提高影片层次的效果<ref>{{cite news | last = Ansen | first = David | title = To Make True Lovers of Friends | work = Newsweek | date = 1989-07-17}}</ref>。

=== 奖项 ===
本片的编剧诺拉·艾芙伦获得了一项[[奥斯卡最佳原著剧本奖|奥斯卡奖提名]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Academy Award Nominations 1989 | publisher = Academy of Motion Picture Arts and Sciences | year = 1989 | url = http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/62nd-winners.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131224025524/http://www.oscars.org/awards/academyawards/legacy/ceremony/62nd-winners.html | archive-date = 2013-12-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和一项[[美国编剧工会奖|美国编剧工会奖]]提名。她赢得了第43届英国电影学院奖最佳原著剧本奖，该片也赢得最佳影片奖提名<ref>{{cite news | title = Film Nominations 1989 | publisher = BAFTA | year = 1989 | url = http://awards.bafta.org/award/1990/film | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305074044/http://awards.bafta.org/award/1990/film | archive-date = 2016-03-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《当哈利碰上莎莉》还获得了5项[[金球奖_(影视奖项)|金球奖]]提名，包括[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧电影|最佳影片（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]、[[金球奖最佳导演|导演]]（罗布·莱纳）、[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影男主角|电影男主角（音乐剧/喜剧类）]]（比利·克里斯托）、[[金球奖最佳音乐及喜剧类电影女主角|电影女主角]]（梅格·瑞安）和[[金球奖最佳剧本|编剧]]（诺拉·艾芙伦）<ref name="globes">{{cite news | title = Browse Results | publisher = Golden Globe Awards Official Website | url = http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=/year/1989 | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130611170739/http://www.goldenglobes.org/browse/?param=%2Fyear%2F1989 | archive-date = 2013-06-11 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

=== 影响 ===
多年以来，《当哈利碰上莎莉》已经成为“现代电影中的精髓，既让人自我感觉良好，又不知何故包含了真理”<ref name="tan">{{cite news | last = Tan | first = Cheryl Lu-Lien | title = ''When Harry Met Sally'': For some, it's become a film icon | work = The Baltimore Sun | date = 2001-02-16 | url = http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20010216&slug=harry16 | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303193312/http://community.seattletimes.nwsource.com/archive/?date=20010216&slug=harry16 | archive-date = 2016-03-03 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。艾芙伦仍然在不断收到对这部电影感到着迷的观众来信，而且还“总是有人来对我说，‘我曾和他或她有过哈利和莎莉式的关系’。”<ref name="tan"/> 2000年，[[美国影艺协会|美国影艺协会]]评选[[AFI百年百大喜剧电影|AFI百年百大喜剧电影]]，本片名列第23位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/100years/laughs.aspx |title=AFI's 100 YEARS...100 LAUGHS |publisher=American Film Institute |accessdate=2013-07-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150609223257/http://www.afi.com/100Years/laughs.aspx |archive-date=2015-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2002年评选[[AFI百年百大爱情电影|AFI百年百大爱情电影]]，本片名列第25位<ref>{{cite web |publisher=American Film Institute |accessdate=2013-07-12 |url=http://www.afi.com/100Years/passions.aspx |title=AFI's 100 YEARS...100 PASSIONS |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306103222/http://afi.com/100years/passions.aspx |archive-date=2016-03-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2004年评选[[AFI百年百大电影歌曲|AFI百年百大电影歌曲]]，本片插曲《{{lang|en|It Had to Be You}}》排名第60位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/100Years/songs.aspx |accessdate=2013-07-12 |publisher=American Film Institute |title=AFI's 100 YEARS...100 SONGS |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306073718/http://afi.com/100Years/songs.aspx |archive-date=2016-03-06 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2005年评选[[AFI百年百大电影台词|AFI百年百大电影台词]]，片中莎莉在餐厅里伪装性高潮后，一位老太太面对服务员询问自己要点什么菜时的回答：“我要点和她一样的”（{{lang|en|I'll have what she's having}}）这句台词名列第33位<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.afi.com/100Years/quotes.aspx |title=AFI's 100 YEARS...100 MOVIE QUOTES |accessdate=2013-07-12 |publisher=American Film Institute |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150415022946/http://www.afi.com/100Years/quotes.aspx |archive-date=2015-04-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，2008年评选[[AFI十大类型大大佳片|AFI十大类型大大佳片]]，《当哈利碰上莎莉》在浪漫喜剧片类型中名列第6位<ref>{{cite news | publisher = American Film Institute | title = AFI's 10 Top 10 | date = 2008-06-17 | url = http://www.afi.com/10top10/romanticcomedy.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080619174502/http://www.afi.com/10top10/romanticcomedy.html | archive-date = 2008-06-19 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

2006年，[[美国精彩电视台|美国精彩电视台]]评选“100部最好笑的电影”，本片名列第60位<ref name="bravo">{{cite news|title=Bravo's 100 Funniest Films |publisher=Boston.com |date=2006-07-25 |url=http://themoviepage.net/bravo100funnyfilms1.html |accessdate=2009-01-05 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090106134641/http://themoviepage.net/bravo100funnyfilms1.html |archivedate=2009-01-06 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。《[[娱乐周刊|娱乐周刊]]》于2002年初将《当哈利碰上莎莉》列入史上最优秀的十部浪漫爱情片之一<ref name="ewtop10">{{cite news|title=Top 10 Romantic Movies |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2002-01-29 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,198095_8,00.html |accessdate=2013-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621150114/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0%2C%2C198095_8%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-21 }}</ref>，之后又于2008年将之评为过去25年中最好笑电影的第12名<ref name="ewtop25">{{cite news|title=The Comedy 25: The Funniest Movies of the Past 25 Years |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-08-27 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20221235_13,00.html |accessdate=2013-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621142258/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20221235_13%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-21 }}</ref>，同年评选的过去25年中最浪漫的电影，本片也名列第7位<ref name="ewtoprom25">{{cite news|title=25 Best Romantic Movies of the Past 25 Years |work=Entertainment Weekly |date=2008-09-11 |url=http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0,,20224567_18,00.html |accessdate=2013-07-12 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621151908/http://www.ew.com/ew/gallery/0%2C%2C20224567_18%2C00.html |archivedate=2013-06-21 }}</ref>，现代浪漫爱情片中更排名第3位<ref name="TopRomances">{{cite news | title=Top 25 Modern Romances | work=Entertainment Weekly | date=2002-02-08 | url=http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,252562,00.html | accessdate=2013-07-12 | first1=Kristen | last1=Baldwin | first2=Scott | last2=Brown | first3=Ty | last3=Burr | first4=Clarissa | last4=Cruz | first5=Amy | last5=Feitelberg | first6=Nicholas | last6=Fonseca | first7=Caroline | last7=Kepnes | first8=Alice M. | last8=Lee | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130621154200/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,252562,00.html | archive-date=2013-06-21 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。在[[烂蕃茄|烂蕃茄]]上的25部最佳浪漫喜剧片中，本片也名列第15位<ref name="rottencom">{{cite news | title = 25 Best Romantic Comedies | publisher = Rotten Tomatoes | year = 2009 | url = http://www.rottentomatoes.com/guides/best_romantic_comedies/when_harry_met_sally/ | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121227093749/http://www.rottentomatoes.com/guides/best_romantic_comedies/when_harry_met_sally/ | archive-date = 2012-12-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《当哈利碰上莎莉》给了许多浪漫喜剧以灵感，包括《[[再见钟情|再见钟情]]》<ref name="hobson">{{cite news | last = Hobson | first = Louis B | title = Flick reminiscent of ''When Harry Met Sally'' | work = Calgary Sun | date = 2005-04-22 | url = http://jam.canoe.ca/Movies/Reviews/A/A_Lot_Like_Love/2005/04/22/pf-1007688.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130624082417/http://jam.canoe.ca/Movies/Reviews/A/A_Lot_Like_Love/2005/04/22/pf-1007688.html | archive-date = 2013-06-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>、 《{{link-en|我和你 (印度电影)|Hum Tum|我和你}}》<ref name=humtum>{{cite news | last = Shariff | first = Faisal | title = Pehli nazar mein pehla pyaar is crap! | work = The Rediff Interview/Kunal Kohli | publisher = Rediff.com | date = 2004-05-27 | url = http://in.rediff.com/movies/2004/may/27kunal.htm | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140730133441/http://in.rediff.com/movies/2004/may/27kunal.htm | archive-date = 2014-07-30 | dead-url = no }}</ref>和《[[爱情三选一|爱情三选一]]》等<ref name="rocchi">{{cite news|last=Rocchi |first=James |title=Review: ''Definitely, Maybe'' |publisher=''Cinematical'' |date=2008-02-14 |url=http://www.cinematical.com/2008/02/14/review-definitely-maybe/ |accessdate=2008-06-22 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080215091211/http://www.cinematical.com/2008/02/14/review-definitely-maybe/ |archivedate=2008-02-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。此外，这部电影捧红了许多有关爱情的理念，像“高维修”女友以及“过渡人士”之后都已经成为家喻户晓的概念<ref name="karpel" />。

2004年初，根据本片改编的舞台剧上演，卢克·贝里和艾莉森·汉尼根分别出演男、女主角<ref>{{cite news|last=Inverne |first=James |title=Hannigan and Perry's ''Harry and Sally'' Set to Face the London Press |publisher=Playbill |date=2004-02-20 |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/84473-Hannigan-and-Perrys-Harry-and-Sally-Set-to-Face-the-London-Press |accessdate=2013-07-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140103193617/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/84473-Hannigan-and-Perrys-Harry-and-Sally-Set-to-Face-the-London-Press |archivedate=2014-01-03 }}</ref>，[[莫利·林沃德|莫利·林沃德]]和[[迈克尔·兰德斯|迈克尔·兰德斯]]后来取代贝里和汉尼根出演了之后的场次<ref>{{cite news|last=Inverne |first=James |title=Landes Joins Ringwald For London ''When Harry Met Sally'' |publisher=Playbill |date=2004-05-17 |url=http://www.playbill.com/news/article/86191-Landes-Joins-Ringwald-For-London-When-Harry-Met-Sally |accessdate=2013-07-15 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120927021358/http://www.playbill.com/news/article/86191-Landes-Joins-Ringwald-For-London-When-Harry-Met-Sally |archivedate=2012-09-27 }}</ref>。

2010年，[[英國|英國]][[衛報|衛報]]評選出有史以來最佳的愛情電影25名，本片名列第22名<ref>{{cite web The 25 best romantic films of all time + Romance films |url= https://www.theguardian.com/film/series/the-romance-25+romance?page=2 {{Wayback|url=https://www.theguardian.com/film/series/the-romance-25+romance?page=2 |date=20200716104509 }}</ref>。

== 家用媒体 ==
《当哈利遇到莎莉》于1989年末电影院上映几个月后首度发行[[VHS|VHS]][[录像带|录像带]]。并于1994年作为比利·克里斯托作品收藏的一部分重新发行了VHS<ref>{{cite article|title=Billboard |date=1994-05-21 |page=55}}</ref>。2001年1月9日影片首次发行[[DVD|DVD]]，其中增加了导演莱纳的评论音轨，还有一段35分钟长的纪录片，其中有对莱纳、艾芙伦、克里斯托、瑞安的采访，7段删除镜头，以及小亨利·康尼克的《{{lang|en|It had to be you}}》音乐录像<ref>{{cite news | last = Richter | first = Erin | title = ''When Harry Met Sally...'': Special Edition | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2001-01-12 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,279400,00.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130621141805/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,279400,00.html | archive-date = 2013-06-21 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2008年1月15日发行了一个收藏版，其中包括莱纳、艾芙伦和克里斯托的新评论音轨，8段删除镜头，并且与之前发行中包含的7段完全不同，还有电影发行的预告片<ref name="karpel">{{cite news | last = Karpel | first = Ari | title = ''When Harry Met Sally'': Collector's Edition | work = Entertainment Weekly | date = 2008-01-11 | url = http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20170537,00.html | accessdate = 2013-07-12 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130524015504/http://www.ew.com/ew/article/0,,20170537,00.html | archive-date = 2013-05-24 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。2011年7月15日本片发行了[[蓝光影碟|蓝光影碟]]，其中包括2008年DVD中的全部内容<ref>{{cite web|last=Reuben|first=Michael|title=When Harry Met Sally Blu-ray Review|url=http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/When-Harry-Met-Sally-Blu-ray/25490/#Review|publisher=Blu-ray.com|accessdate=2012-09-13|date=2013-07-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120918030014/http://www.blu-ray.com/movies/When-Harry-Met-Sally-Blu-ray/25490/#Review|archive-date=2012-09-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

